title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 14: Brendon Walsh is UnCERNtain About This Podcast
description:
Thanks for tuning into another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. Today guest is Brendon Walsh and he was not impressed with my podcast or our subject, CERN! On this episode we discuss...
1)The Ecuadorian Election
2) Chinese/Russian Currency
3) The Strongsville Adoption Agency and The Clintons
Then we get into
4) CERN
5) Book of Revelations 9-11
6) Solar Axion Telescopic Antenna AKA SATAN
7)Dr. Edward Mantill
This is definitely one of the weirder episodes I have done. I hope you enjoy this episode more the Brendon. Thank you so much for your support!
